9716325 |title=What life is like on Antarctica, the only continent without a case of coronavirus |work=ABC News |access-date=31 March 2020}}</ref>||{{flagicon|Antarctica}} [[Antarctic Treaty System]]||[[Antarctica]]\n|-\n|2||{{flagicon|British Indian Ocean Territory}} [[Diego Garcia]]||colspan=\"2\"| {{Nts|4239}}||{{flag|British Indian Ocean Territory}}||{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United Kingdom|United Kingdom]]||[[Asia]]\n|-\n|3||{{flagicon|French Southern and Antarctic Lands}} [[Kerguelen Islands]]||{{Nts|110}}||{{Nts|45}}||{{flag|French Southern and Antarctic Lands}}||{{flagicon|France}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in France|France]]||[[Africa]]\n|-\n|4||{{flag|Wake Island|local}}||colspan=\"2\"| {{nts|100}}||{{flag|United States Minor Outlying Islands}}||{{flagicon|United States}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United States|United States]]||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|5||{{flagicon|French Southern and Antarctic Lands}} [[Scattered Islands in the Indian Ocean]]||colspan=\"2\"| {{nts|56}}||{{flag|French Southern and Antarctic Lands}}||{{flagicon|France}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in France|France]]||[[Africa]]\n|-\n|6||{{flag|Midway Atoll|local}}||colspan=\"2\"| {{nts|40}}||{{flag|United States Minor Outlying Islands}}||{{flagicon|United States}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United States|United States]]||[[Oceania]]\n|-\n|7||{{flag|Jan Mayen}}||colspan=\"2\"| {{Nts|35}}||{{flagicon|Norway}} [[Svalbard and Jan Mayen]]||{{flagicon|Norway}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Norway|Norway]]||[[Europe]]\n|-\n|8||{{flagicon|South Georgia and the South Sandwich Islands}} [[South Georgia Island]]||{{Nts|32}}||{{Nts|16}}||{{flag|South Georgia and the South Sandwich Islands}}||{{flagicon|United Kingdom}} [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in the United Kingdom|United Kingdom]]||[[South America]]\n|-\n|9||{{flagicon|French Southern and Antarctic Lands}} [[Crozet Islands]]||{{Nts|30}}||{{Nts|18}}||{{flag|French Southern and Antarctic Lands}}||{{f