ricanreviewr09shawgoog#page/n61/mode/2up \u201cExit Constantine,\u201d] ''The American Review of Reviews'', Vol. LVI, July/December 1917.\n* [https://archive.org/stream/americanreviewr09shawgoog#page/n503/mode/2up \u201cRussia: A Bird\u2019s-Eye View,\u201d] ''The American Review of Reviews'', Vol. LVI, July/December 1917.\n\n{{Col-3}}\n* [https://archive.org/stream/unpopularreview09newyrich#page/384/mode/2up \u201cSome Reflections on Revolution,\u201d] ''The Unpopular Review'', Vol. IX, January/June, 1918.\n* [https://archive.org/stream/americanreviewr01unkngoog#page/n300/mode/2up \u201cRussia and German Policy,\u201d] ''The American Review of Reviews'', Vol. LVIII, July/December, 1918.\n* [https://archive.org/stream/worldswork37gard#page/350/mode/2up \u201cWhat Remains of Germanism in Central Europe,\u201d] ''The American Review of Reviews'', Vol. XXXVII, November 1918/April 1919.\n* [https://archive.org/stream/worldswork37gard#page/398/mode/2up \u201cPeace Conferences that Have Failed in the Past,\u201d] ''The American Review of Reviews'', Vol. XXXVII, November 1918/April 1919.\n* [https://archive.org/stream/worldswork38gard#page/n29/mode/2up \u201cThe World as It Is,\u201d] [https://archive.org/stream/worldswork38gard#page/204/mode/2up Part II,] [https://archive.org/stream/worldswork38gard#page/276/mode/2up Part III,] [https://archive.org/stream/worldswork38gard#page/438/mode/2up Part IV,] [https://archive.org/stream/worldswork38gard#page/470/mode/2up Part V], ''The American Review of Reviews'', Vol. XXXVIII, May 1919.\n* [https://archive.org/stream/worldswork38gard#page/20/mode/2up \u201cThe Economic Foundations of Peace,\u201d] ''The American Review of Reviews'', Vol. XXXVIII, May 1919.\n* [http://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=hvd.32044092637974;view=1up;seq=153 \"Adria: The Troubled Sea,\"] ''The Century Magazine,'' Vol. XCVIII, 1919.\n* [http://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=hvd.32044092637974;view=1up;seq=263 \"Bolshevism: The Heresy of the Underman,\"] ''